<p>Italian fashion designer Valentino Garavani, founder of the Valentino label, has died at age 93 at his home in Rome, his foundation announced. Celebrated for elegant couture and a signature “Valentino red,” he dressed clients ranging from Jacqueline Kennedy Onassis and Princess Diana to generations of Hollywood stars. The news has prompted an outpouring of tributes that highlight his lasting influence on how fashion can help people feel confident and seen.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/HFdY3PQR3j2PzDwf7LamALwl7SWKSFiMiHHUefuE5UjDvaFSHfV0VGGPJAeGGYXeazkPyTUTP-MSCG-c4SrbsoP3ccV5HGioQL7rPa2Q25E3HmYD-OMet_wf9NYsuv55f9sUPsi39lkQpfvnHs9zfwQk9HTic9d7rj1j4ZCLS2OqsPoJxOEV6NTFFXdLpes' alt='Valentino Garavani in 1968.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Lying in state: His foundation said his body will lie in state at its Rome headquarters on Wednesday and Thursday.</li><li>Funeral details: The funeral is scheduled for Friday at the Basilica Santa Maria degli Angeli e dei Martiri in Rome.</li><li>Brand partnership: Valentino met Giancarlo Giammetti in 1960, with Giammetti running business operations while Valentino led design.</li><li>Sale and retirement: The label was sold to an Italian holding company for an estimated $300 million in 1998, and Valentino remained involved in design until retiring in 2008.</li><li>Creative succession: Semafor noted the brand has been under designer Alessandro Michele since 2024, amid broader leadership changes across European luxury houses.</li></ul><blockquote>Valentino Garavani was not only a constant guide and inspiration for all of us, but a true source of light, creativity and vision. - Valentino Garavani’s foundation</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Valentino Garavani’s foundation: The foundation announced his death in Rome and portrayed him as a continuing inspiration to those who worked with him and support his legacy. (<a href='https://www.npr.org/2026/01/19/1114518694/valentino-garavani-dead'>NPR</a>)</li><li>Giancarlo Giammetti: His longtime partner shared a personal tribute on Instagram, posting a photo captioned “forever.”. (<a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/true-maestro-tributes-flow-for-fashionisto-valentino/'>Michael West</a>)</li><li>Donatella Versace: Versace described Valentino as “a true maestro” and expressed sympathy for Giammetti, saying he “will never be forgotten.”. (<a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/true-maestro-tributes-flow-for-fashionisto-valentino/'>Michael West</a>)</li><li>Alessandro Michele: The current creative director said he continues to feel Valentino’s presence as he works on upcoming collections. (<a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/valentino-made-royals-and-movie-stars-feel-beautiful/'>Michael West</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.npr.org/2026/01/19/1114518694/valentino-garavani-dead'>Italian fashion designer Valentino dies at 93</a> - npr.org</li><li><a href='https://www.rt.com/pop-culture/631182-valentino-fashion-legend-dies/'>Italian fashion legend Valentino dies at 93</a> - rt.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c4gwkdm2w33o'>In pictures: Valentino&#x27;s life and work - and the stars who shared his journey</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/obituaries/article/2026/01/19/valentino-garavani-fashion-designer-who-founded-valentino-dies-at-93_6749585_15.html'>Valentino Garavani, fashion designer who founded Valentino, dies at 93</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3340477/valentino-fashion-designer-stars-dies-aged-93-rome'>Valentino, fashion designer to the jet set, stars and royalty, dead at 93</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://michaelwest.com.au/valentino-made-royals-and-movie-stars-feel-beautiful/'>Valentino made royals and movie stars feel beautiful</a> - michaelwest.com.au</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/valentino-garavani-dies-age-93-designer/'>Valentino Garavani, iconic fashion designer, dies at age 93</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/01/19/2026/valentino-fashions-last-emperor-dies-at-93'>Valentino, fashion&#x27;s ‘last emperor,’ dies at 93</a> - semafor.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/life-and-style/fashion/valentino-garavani-fashion-designer-to-jet-set-dies-aged-93-in-rome/article70527070.ece'>Valentino Garavani, fashion designer to jet set, dies aged 93 in Rome</a> - thehindu.com</li></ul>